title: Jenn-Air JX3 Gas Downdraft Cooktop JGD3536 Overview
description:
Jenn-Air 36  JX3 Stainless Steel Gas Downdraft Cooktop - http://www.abt.com/product/74565/Jenn-Air-JGD3536BS.html

Features:
• Industrys Best Performing Ventilation System
• JX3™ Downdraft Ventilation System with 3-Speed Fan
• Convertible to Duct-Free Ventilation
• 17000 BTU Ultra-High Output Burner
• Electronic Ignition and Flame-Sensing™ Re-ignition
• Five Sealed Burners
• 425 CFM Rating
• Easy-to-Clean Short Plenum
• Dishwasher-Safe Air Grill
• Dishwasher-Safe Burner Grates and Caps
• Infinite Burner Control Settings
• Porcelain-on-Cast-Iron Grates
• Porcelain-Enamel/Stainless Steel Surface
